sectionText: This course will open to all students in the College of Business on Monday, November 14, 2016 and to business minors on Monday, November 21, 2016 at approximately 9:00 a.m.  This course will open to Informatics Minors on Monday, November 28, 2016 at approximately 9:00 a.m.  There are currently 5 reserved seats for College of Business international exchange students; any unused seats will be released to students meeting the restrictions on Friday, January 20, 2017.  This is an elective course for undergraduate students pursuing the business minor.
